column5:
Added events (liszt:hiding_dropdown, liszt:showing_dropdown) to dropdown hiding/showing to support custom event scenarios and inextricable z-index problems
usage:
mySelect.chosen()
mySelect.bind('liszt:showing_dropdown', function() { someOtherObject.hide(); });
mySelect.bind('liszt:hiding_dropdown', function() { someOtherObject.show(); });
